---
title: Crispy Monterey Jack Chicken with Buttery Green Beans, Potato Wedges, and Spicy Mayo
description: Crispy chicken is always a recipe for success. Add melty Monterey Jack and Ranch seasoning to the mix and you’ve got yourself a winning dinner. Once baked, the cheesy panko crust turns golden brown while the meat stays juicy and tender. The crunchy cutlets are served with sriracha-spiked mayo and sides of buttery green beans and crispy potato wedges. If this all sounds complicated—it’s not! 35 minutes is all you need for this delicious dish to land on your table.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crispy-monterey-jack-chicken-8bca3280.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/crispy-monterey-jack-chicken-5d517cd67cb153000b183ba2-e60befa8.pdf
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
course: main course
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 790 kcal
  fat: 50 g
  saturated fat: 16 g
  carbohydrates: 40 g
